reviewText: It didn't work i'ts waist of time and money to return it selling DVD that not working in US it's like deceiving customers.

While this film has some value for its humorous portrayal of a man's life, for me it did not live up to the high ratings I had read.  Definitely not in sync with the modern era, outdated.  In choosing to view this film I was influenced mainly by the director Lubitsch.  In this case I felt let down.  Ameche's performance, however,  was very professional and worthy of praise.
